{"tid":58875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【南港島綫停電】斥職員安排混亂 乘客：全車乘客要落車","createTime":"2016-12-29T07:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T09:04:27.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d992a95f54799fe7508bd470841c9acd0ddb4c7","tid":58875,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161229/large/1482996512_cdb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161229%2Flarge%2F1482996512_cdb4.jpg&h=9cc98c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵南港島綫通車第二日，即發生停電延誤事故。乘客黃先生當時在黃竹坑站，乘坐南港島綫到金鐘處理公務，豈料遇上停電事故，最終4個站的車程花上近半小時，大失預算。<br />\n<br />\n黃先生指，當時一入黃竹坑站便見站內的扶手電梯﹑升降機及電燈等全部停止運作，閘門打開，乘客不需付款入閘。到達月台後，等候約10分鐘才登上列車。但列車駛至海洋公園站再次停駛，全車乘客需下車等侯5分鐘，才能再次登車前往金鐘。過程中，職員安排混亂，亦未能說出事故原因，少量趕時間的乘客表現鼓譟。<br />\n<br />\n經此事後，黃先生對港鐵南港島線的服務感到失望，「難得通到車，咁短時間就有問題，如果係繁忙時間就大件事喇。」他希望港鐵做好機件的檢查及維修，並訓練員工對事故的應變能力，提升市民的信心。"},{"pid":"e9d2dc9f71987fc3b24a71120a1bc3063e1bef79","tid":58875,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:36:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4eb44963edd5bbd4fdf62de7fc9fab46d96c8da","tid":58875,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:36:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5db8130d0fdb5447634502150254bad1514a9baa","tid":58875,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:37:00.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"06433b47168a7e1269054c01c4d61142ebd2112d","tid":58875,"uid":15607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60cffcc6b7fc43ec168dd6cdc5685940730ea06c","tid":58875,"uid":34192,"li